Communications Advisor and Co-Founder, The Comms Avenue, Adedoyin Jaiyesimi, has unveiled the Comms Simplified series to equip communications professionals with information and tool required to achieve the best results. 
 
Speaking during the launch, she said the teaching series would provide a platform for communications professionals to access information, templates and guides required to do excellent work and deliver valuable results.  Jaiyesimi added that a Comms KPI Guide also accompanied the video and it provides tools professionals can use to measure the metrics that are important to their organisation. 